author: Bruce Lee
message: The less effort, the faster and more powerful you will be.

author: Ralph Emerson
message: We must be as courteous to a man as we are to a picture, which we are willing to give the advantage of a good light.

author: Anais Nin
message: The dream was always running ahead of me. To catch up, to live for a moment in unison with it, that was the miracle.

message: The cure for boredom is curiosity. There is no cure for curiosity.
